titles.title: A resolution notifying the House of Representatives of the election of a Secretary of the Senate.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 4/19/1994--Introduced. Notifies the House of Representatives of the election of the Honorable Martha S. Pope as Secretary of the Senate.
